n produced the nora roberts ii collection with four more allnew original movies northern lights midnight bayou high noon and tribute the second collection was seen by over  million viewers and northern lights was one of the top rated cable movies in  mandalay television completed the ninth installment in the franchise carnal innocence starring gabrielle anwar which premiered on lifetime in june  mandalay sports entertainmentedit peter guber serves as chairman of the board of directors and is the managing partner of mandalay baseball llc which is a joint venture with ownership of the los angeles dodgers that recently acquired the triplea affiliated minor league baseball franchise in oklahoma city and commencing with the  baseball season will become the triplea affiliate of the dodgers he also continues to serve as the chairman of the board of directors for mandalay baseball properties which has owned operated and is currently divesting a national array of affiliated minor league baseball franchises and venues among the professional sports franchises that have been recently divested by mandalay baseball properties are the dayton dragons a singlea affiliate of the cincinnati reds which broke the alltime north american professional sports record for consecutive sell outs in  with  games encompassing  seasons and in august  was sold for the highest price ever paid for a minor league baseball franchise mandalay baseball properties continues to own and operate the erie seawolves a doublea affiliate of the detroit tigers mandalay sports mediaedit in  guber and mandalay entertainment partnered with caa sports and mike tollin to create mandalay sports media the sports media business creates finances and acquires operating businesses intellectual property and varied enterprises within the sports and media sectors as well as develops sportsthemed entertainment programming for distribution across film television mobile and digital in october  mandalay sports media invested in and became the largest shareholder in oyo sports a “fan engagement” company that produces buildable minireplicas of athletes from major professional sports leagues including the mlb nfl nhl and mls as well as some universities dick clark productionsedit in september  peter guber and mandalay entertainment joined a partnership which purchased dick clark productions from red zone capital management their productions include specials like the golden globes the american music awards the academy of country music awardsnew years rockin eve and reality show so you think you can dance golden state warriorsedit peter guber serves as the coexecutive chairman of the golden state warriors as comanaging partner he joined joe lacob as the driving forces behind the current ownership group’s nba recordsetting bid to purchase the warriors in  the warriors won the nba championships for the  nba season and  nba season consultant marc ganis said of the purchase “this could be one of the most valuable teams in the nba” the golden state warriors won the  sports business journal award for team of the year saying the team “continued a sharp trajectory in  under owners joe lacob and peter guber that produced strong extensive on and offcourt gains” guber and lacob agreed to buy  acres of land in san franciscos mission bay neighborhood to build a privately financed new arena the move would mark the warrior’s return to a home arena in san francisco from oakland for the first time in more than four decades opening is targeted for the  season lacob said of guber he cares more than any owner about the team the image of the team and what the fans think los angeles dodgersedit on march   guber became an owner of the los angeles dodgers as a partner in guggenheim baseball entertainment the los angeles dodgers clinched the  national league west division championship and played postseason baseball for the first time since  guber was persuaded to join the group purchasing the dodgers by magic johnson “magic called and he said ‘come on we’ve been so lucky together we’ve been so good together let’s do it let’s do it let’s do it’ ” said guber so after meeting with johnson and others in the prospective ownership group guber decided to join the team that would make the  billion winning offer which more than doubled the previous record price for a north american sports franchise” howard nuchow cohead of caa sports described guber’s contributions as attached to the entire baseball experience its the notion peter has that you have to entertain fans from the time they receive tickets in the mail until they drive home los angeles football clubedit in october  peter guber became the owner and executive chairman of major league soccers los angeles football club lafc the ownership group includes entrepreneur henry nguyen sports veteran tom penn earvin magic johnson mia hamm garciaparra and tony robbins among others the new club is scheduled to debut in  in a new soccer stadium in the greater los angeles area built specifically for the team authoredit gubers most recent book tell to win  connect persuade and triumph with the hidden power of story became a  bestseller in the new york times usa today the wall street journal fortune magazine chose tell to win as one of their  business books you can really use  peter guber’s other books include inside the deep and the los angeles times bestseller shootout surviving fame and misfortune in hollywood guber authored a cover piece for the harvard business review and oped pieces for the new york times professoredit peter guber is a professor at the ucla school of theater film television and digital media and has been a member of the faculty for over  years he also teaches at uclas anderson school of management he is a member of the ucla foundation board of trustees as well as the winner of uclas service award for his accomplishments and association with the university guber is the chair of the founding board of advisors for the center for managing enterprises in media entertainment  sports memes at the ucla anderson school of management  of his course guber said “i wanted students to recognize the power of narrative he said storytelling is not frivolous entertainment its an inspirational and professional tool that can bring life into focus  speakeredit in  guber was named one of the “twelve great speakers of the year” by successful meetings magazine guber’s national and global speaking events include cisco jwt under armour alcoa hsbc twitter sodexo milken institute intel korn ferry womens wear daily ceo summit wharton leadership conference gap inc john hancock life insurance experian marketing del monte foods cox media group comcast league of legends team ownershipedit in  bruce stein along with guber and his group axiomatic purchased team liquid a professional american league of legends team  films producededit the deep  producer midnight express  executive producer an american werewolf in london  executive producer missing  executive producer six weeks  producer flashdance  executive producer dc cab  executive producer vision quest  producer the legend of billie jean  executive producer clue  executive producer the color purple  executive producer head office  executive producer the clan of the cave bear  executive producer youngblood  executive producer the witches of eastwick  producer innerspace  executive producer whos that girl  executive producer caddyshack ii  producer gorillas in the mist  executive producer missing link  executive producer rain man   executive producer batman  producer tango  cash  producer the bonfire of the vanities  executive producer batman returns  executive producer this boys life  executive producer with honors  executive producer sleepy hollow  producer the score  producer enemy at the gates  producer serving sara  producer alex and emma  executive producer beyond borders  producer into the blue  executive producer the jacket  producer a thousand roads  executive 